December 31, 2019. At December 31, 2021, the Company had net operating loss carryforwards of
approximately $60.5 million. Of this amount, $35.2 million may be carried forward indefinitely. The
remaining $25.3 million of net operating loss carryforwards will begin to expire in 2022.
