Corporate and unallocated amounts that do not relate to a reportable segment have been allocated
to “Corporate & Unallocated.” No asset information, other than goodwill and other intangible assets, has
been provided in the Company’s reportable segments, as management does not measure or allocate such
assets on a segment basis.
